extendedInfo.description: Now with new themes, weather effects, butterflies, and more - your favorite Live Wallpaper is now even better!Inspired by a visit to Ireland, discover a hidden grove nestled deep in an enchanted forest. This serene, calming garden scene with a Celtic flare will brighten your day wherever you go. Customize from hundreds of possible combinations to make this beautiful garden your own!Perfect for St. Patrick's day - or any time of the year!This live wallpaper features a verdant animated Irish forest with a charming fountain in the center. The three-dimensional dynamic scene includes animated water, shamrocks, cascading sunlight, and more. Tap the screen to cause fireflies and fairies to float through your garden.Works great with phones, tablets, or any device that supports live wallpapers.

reviews.title: Love this live wallpaper, but ...
reviews.comment: Fantastic graphics, toggle options are wonderful. One oversight:The panning doesn\'t include the leafy background. Therefore, it looks as if the foreground slowly spins as if on a Lazy Susan. But you know something? It\'s still great - thank you!

reviews.title: Serene, peaceful and beautiful
